name: CatTranslator
0:
”Alexa, open cat translator.”
”Alexa, launch cat translator.”
”Alexa, ask cat translator why Daisy is sneezing.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat translator
des: Have you ever wondered why your cat rubs her tail against your legs, demands attention while you're staring at your phone, or jumps on the dinner table while you're trying to enjoy a meal? This skill can help you understand why your cat does the weird things they do. Just tell Alexa your cat's behavior and she will scan the vast network of super scientific, smarty pants answers and deliver them with a heavy helping of sass- proof that she really can speak cat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
